external_knowledge:
- The metaphorical expression "seeds of creation" refers to products;
- "Fertile ground of the United States" refers to suppliers located in the United States;
- "Nurturing the garden of commerce" implies contributing to the market or commercial activities.

sql:
SELECT s_name, s_rating
FROM suppliers
ORDER BY s_rating DESC;

SELECT s_name, AVG(s_rating) AS average_rating
FROM suppliers
GROUP BY s_name;

external_knowledge:
- Highly-rated suppliers: suppliers with a rating greater than 3;
- Made orders recently: orders placed in the past month;
- Typical delivery speed: average delivery time in days;
- Product quality: average quality rating from 1 to 5.

sql:
SELECT s_name, s_acctbal, s_rating
FROM suppliers
ORDER BY s_acctbal DESC;

SELECT po_supplierkey, COUNT(po_orderkey) AS total_orders
FROM purchase_orders
GROUP BY po_supplierkey;
